# helper to config the right time: https://crontab.guru/

# Min  Hour Day  Mon  Weekday
# *    *    *    *    *  command to be executed
# ┬    ┬    ┬    ┬    ┬
# │    │    │    │    └─  Day of Week   (0=Sun .. 6=Sat)
# │    │    │    └──────  Month         (1..12)
# │    │    └───────────  Day of Month  (1..31)
# │    └────────────────  Hour          (0..23)
# └─────────────────────  Minute        (0..59)

# chain script in sequence
# 0 * * * * myScript.sh && nexScript.sh && anotherScript.sh

